bug.short_desc: TreeVirtual resizing can lead to additional columns disappearance

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1233 test application
Run the attached test application. Firstly, try to move splitter slightly to the left (for example, by 20-30 px). You will see that the tree have rendered correctly. Next, try to move splitter on a distance that is much more than the total width of additional columns (for example, by 200-300 px). As a result the second and third column will be out of sight (invisible).
